  <h1 class="title topictitle1">sql avg()</h1>

  <div class="body">
    <div class="section"><h2 class="title sectiontitle">avg() function</h2>
      <p class="p">Be userd to calculate average for all values of the specified field.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="section"><h2 class="title sectiontitle">Grammar</h2>
      <div class="p"><pre class="pre codeblock">avg(field_name) as &lt;alisa_name&gt;</pre>
</div>

      <div class="note note"><span class="notetitle">Note:</span> 1.When use avg function to calculate average for the field , you must use alisa name
          .<p class="p">2.It will auto skip for non-numeric .</p>
</div>

    </div>

    <div class="section"><h2 class="title sectiontitle">Sample</h2>
      <ul class="ul">
        <li class="li"><p class="p">calculating  average for the field name <em class="ph i">age</em> in the collection <em class="ph i">bar</em>.</p>

          <div class="p"><pre class="pre codeblock">db.exec("select avg(age) as 平均年龄 from foo.bar")</pre>
</div>

        </li>

      </ul>

    </div>

  </div>

